# Loan Status Prediction 💰

A Machine Learning project that predicts whether a loan application will be **Approved** or **Rejected**.

## Dataset

- **Size:** 3,192 samples
- **Features:** 12 input features (Gender, Income, Age, Credit History, etc.)
- **Target:** Loan_Status (Approved or Rejected)

## Models Tested

| Model | Accuracy | Precision | Recall | F1 Score |
|-------|----------|-----------|--------|----------|
| **Random Forest** | **98.44%** | **100%** | **96.97%** | **0.9846** |
| Logistic Regression | 98.12% | 99.38% | 96.97% | 0.9816 |
| Support Vector Machine | 49.14% | 52.38% | 16.67% | 0.2529 |

## 🏆 Best Model: Random Forest

- **Accuracy:** 98.44%
- **Precision:** 100%
- **Recall:** 96.97%
- **F1 Score:** 0.9846

